column9: no effect of background noise on your ability to hear nightjars
slightly affects your ability to hear nightjars (e.g. distant traffic, 1-2 car passing during a counting period).
moderately affects your ability to hear nightjars (e.g. nearby traffic, 3-6 cars passing during survey period, airplane flying overhead).
seriously affects your ability to hear nightjars (e.g. continuous traffic nearby, construction noise, frog chorus)
Can see stars and moon clearly
Few clouds, less than 25% cloud cover
Dense cloud cover, entire sky covered. Should not conduct survey.
